							<view class="w-[8rpx] h-[8rpx] rounded-[2rpx] bg-[#0052d9] mt-[14rpx] shrink-0"></view>
							<text class="flex-1 text-[26rpx] text-[#646a73] leading-[36rpx]">任务金额将在审核通过后冻结，任务完成后自动结算</text>
